  "original_title": "\u0b9a\u0bc7\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0bb5\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b8e\u0bae\u0bcd.\u0baa\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "MP who voted with Saline Bothal",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In this case, MP Saman Priya Herath, who had recovered, came inside the House with Saline Bothal.",
        "His name is number 223 in the table. However, the Parliamentary Secretary General asked the House if there were any objections to giving him an opportunity to vote in the interim.",
        "Saline bottle, to be held by an assistant. He voted and left the house."
      ],
